==Latin==

===Etymology===
From {{etyl|ine-pro|la}} {{m|ine-pro|*ád||near, at}}. Cognates include English {{term|at||lang=en}}.

===Pronunciation===
* {{a|Classical}} {{IPA|/ad/|lang=la}}
